title: Hunt Trophy and Floral Arabesque
description: Vertical rectangle of joined sheets of paper. Alternating medallions: one shows two dogs guarding the carcass of a deer hanging head downward from a tree on which hangs also a hunting horn; the other shows a tripod urn containing flowers, flanked by peacock feathers, below which is a nest with three young birds.
